-- Roche Won’t Revisit Illumina Purchase Offer, Chief Tells Sonntag
-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 2012-06-10T12:19:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-10/roche-won-t-revisit-illumina-purchase-offer-chief-tells-sonntag.html
Roche Holding AG (ROG)  will not make a new
purchase offer for  Illumina Inc. (ILMN) , Der Sonntag reported, citing
an interview with Chief Executive Officer Severin Schwan.  Roche is focusing mostly on small and medium-sized
acquisitions, Schwan told the newspaper. He also said he
wouldn’t rule out acquisitions the size of Illumina if
opportunities arise, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elena Logutenkova in Zurich at 
